divs: sighting detailsi was taking my dog out and i was standing at the base of the fir trees and noticed something moving really fast behind the trees about 2\3 the way up the treeline. i caught this of the out of the corner of my eye only because the object was really moving.i never even saw a jet move that fast. i thought it was a falling star so i watched it until it come out from behind the treeline. it moved the span of the whole tree, limb to limb in about 7 seconds and then came out into a clearing. the object seemed to be moving in a straight line(no zig zagging motion)it made 90 degree turn to the left and sped up out of sight. there was no noise at all. it was a few minutes to 9:oopm sept. 18th 2009
